                <note rend="inline" type="source">511.3B1/9: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Commission to Negotiate Peace</gloss>
                        to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-10-25T23:00:00+00:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 25, 1919—11 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received 11:28 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>4824. Your 3469, October 17th, 5 p.m. Commission shares Department’s views as to
                    nature and [effect of] protocol to Arms Traffic Convention, and informal
                    discussion shows that Principal Allied and Associated Powers understand protocol
                    in same sense. Polk.</p>
                <closer>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Mission</hi>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
